                        <p>WCA identifies talented traders and authorizes them to trade “lead” accounts which are funded with their own money. Subscribers pay a monthly fee to "mirror" the account of the leader they choose to follow. To mirror trades, a subscriber must open an account at an authorized broker and fund it at a level appropriate for the program(s) he or she elects to follow. </p>
                    </div>
