                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3">
                    <div class="how-wrk-bx">
                        <img src="~/Content/images/select-search.svg" alt="" />
                        <h3>SEARCH &amp; SELECT</h3>
                        <p>To find a "leader" program that’s right for you in terms of your investment objectives, risk tolerance and funding level simply create a free 14-day trial membership and use our tools: Net-Profit Calculator to view fees and performance, Life-of-program closed trade details, Advisor profiles and specifications, Performance summaries, Detailed month-end performance reports.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3">
                    <div class="how-wrk-bx">
                        <img src="~/Content/images/edit-document.svg" alt="" />
                        <h3>SUBSCRIBE</h3>
                        <p>If you’ve narrowed your search and need more guidance, give us a call so we can help you make a final decision. If you’ve made your decision, click here to start the subscription process.</p>
